</div>well, something else needs to be done instead of drop rate.  We have 5 rogues in guild ( number 1 guild on our server ) , 2 if not 3 have nothing to do with poisons whatsoever, which leaves me and shmoozneak ( he is a very active poisonmaker and poster on these forums ).  I've only gotten 2 pristines from GB, with alot of grade xxx ( this stuff is buyable from vender ), I dont know how much shmooz has gotten, but I tend to think the drop rate is fubar.  I dont think doubling nor tripling is going to be enough.   So I think it would better suit the rogue only quests to have utility only rewards instead of stuff we can buy and make from venders.  Since this is supposed to increase the group rogue DPS mostly.<br />
<br />
How it is now, group rogue asks for a group, group asks, can u slow? no not yet need to farm stuff to slow,  8 hours laters, get first deagro drop, still cant slow yet, 8 hours later get his first slow poison, goes to combine it, fails on first combine, goes and exps for another 8 hours get another one, passes first combine but fails second, 24 hours spent, no utility.  Rogue not really needed because he isnt adding that much to a group as a group rogue.  The drops are so stupidly rare + the under 25-50% combine rate is just stupid.  Yes, I'm having a ton of fun with the dd poisons, still like the single shot even though it got nerfed, but I'm not experiencing any utility poisons yet and I'm very frustrated at this point in the game with it.</div>
