<br />
In fact, a combo poison that does a little bit of snare and a decent chunk of slow would be perhaps one of the best soloing poisons around.  In other words, something a bit like the old Stiffening Ergot poison effect, but with a lesser snare effect than a pure snaring poison and a lesser slow effect than a pure slowing poison would be really nice.  .<br />
