    <div align="left" id="post_message_478203">With a duration of only 6 seconds (acording to lucy) I don't see any of them of being that great.  If I need slow I use a Locustlure (3.5 minutes).  If I need snare I use a Darkened Serrated Bone Dirk (1.5 min, and does damage).  Takes on avg 20-30 sec to proc and I know the effect will last.<br />
<br />
Poisons however proc every 12 sec on avg (2 ppm base, +1 wa,  +1 vv, +1 from poison mod = 5 ppm) and last 6 sec.  If the fight is important enough to warrent the use of a non-trivial to acquire poison, having the effect have a chance of wearing off isn't going to cut it.</div>
