But at 6 ppm base, thats 8 with weapon affinity and virulent venom.  So 6 sec duration proc'ing every 7.5 sec.  20% of the time (1.5 sec every 7.5), on average, the mob won't be slowed.  And leaves you vulnerable to rng streaks a lot more than weapon that is &quot;proc and  forget about it&quot;.<br />
<br />
